OL,4,Cstation gets go-ahead
OL,6,FPlans also include enhanced ticket
OL,7,Fgates to improve access and flow
OL,8,Faround the station and ease links with
OL,9,Fother ways to travel. The Department
OL,10,Ffor Transport also hopes to improve
OL,11,Fwaiting areas, enhance retail
OL,12,Fofferings and cycle storage facilities.
OL,14,FThe station welcomes over 35,000
OL,15,Fpeople a day and thousands more during
OL,16,Fmajor events, such as the Six Nations.
