OL,3,C#140 million revamp for railway
OL,4,Cstation gets go-ahead
OL,6,FAlongside the #445m investment, the
OL,7,FGovernment is providing a further #50m
OL,8,Ffor a new Cardiff Metro station with a
OL,9,Fdirect connection to Cardiff Bay,
OL,10,Fpaving the way for future extension to
OL,11,Fthe north-west and east of Cardiff.
OL,13,FThis project is part of a wider #445m
OL,14,Finvestment from the Department for
OL,15,FTransport to deliver improvements to
OL,16,Frail infrastructure across the whole
OL,17,Fof Wales, including increased train
OL,18,Fservices to Cardiff, new stations in
OL,19,FSouth Wales, and increased services on
OL,20,Fthe North Wales Mainline and Wrexham-
OL,21,FLiverpool line.
