OL,3,C#140 million revamp for railway
OL,4,Cstation gets go-ahead
OL,6,FAlongside the funding, the final
OL,7,Fbusiness case for the transformation
OL,8,Fhas been approved, giving the green
OL,9,Flight for work to get underway in
OL,10,FSpring 2026, with the majority of the
OL,11,Fwork expected to be completed by 2029.
OL,13,FHeidi Alexander, Secretary of State
OL,14,Ffor Transport, said: "The improvements
OL,15,Fto Cardiff Central will transform the
OL,16,Fexperience of the millions of
OL,17,Fpassengers who use the station every
OL,18,Fyear, welcoming people through a
OL,19,Fspacious, modern station befitting of
OL,20,Fthe city it serves.
